- [ ] `-providers` and `-exclude-providers` flags work correctly
- [ ] `ModelRef` type has Provider, RawFamily, Family, Variant, Date fields
- [ ] `ModelInfo.Ref()` returns a ModelRef with RawFamily and Date populated
